parameters.name: START_DATE
parameters.description:
Start date in the format YYDOY where YY is the 2 digit year and DOY    
                        is the day-of-year (Jan 1 = 1)

parameters.name: STOP_DATE
parameters.description:
Date in the form YYDOY where YY is the 2 digit year and the DOY        
                        is the day-of-year (Jan 1 =1).

parameters.name: START_ORBIT
parameters.description: The start orbit number of the 10 orbit record.

parameters.name: STOP_ORBIT
parameters.description: The last orbit of the 10 orbit record.
